citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 8:30am-9:00am on
May 10, 2023. Contact attempts were initially: honking, knocking and leaving a voice message on phone number
provided. An on-site building contractor indicated that they had moved. I finally made contact with licensee to find out
when they are usually at this site.
End Section

Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.

May 10, 2023.  Contact attempts were initially: honking, knocking and leaving a voice message on phone number 
provided.  An on-site building contractor indicated that they had moved. I finally made contact with licensee to find out
